Package: artshiny
Title: Shared Shiny UI Components
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Bobby", "Fatemi", , "bobby@artalytics.app", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides reusable Shiny UI components and helpers for the Artalytics
    platform. Includes shared modules for statistics displays, loading screens,
    and other interface elements used across multiple app modules. Centralizes
    common UI patterns to maintain consistency and reduce code duplication.
